      <h1 class='title'>Sector Skills Council Boundaries</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='commons-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 27 October 2003 vol 412 c86WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_86ws' title='Col. 86WS &mdash; HC Deb 27 October 2003 vol 412 c86WS' name='column_86ws' href='#column_86ws' rel='bookmark'>86WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0412P0-05089'>
        <a name='S6CV0412P0_20031027_CWS2_438'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-tim-boswell' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0412P0_20031027_CWS2_438' title='Link to this speech by Mr Tim Boswell' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-tim-boswell" title="Mr Tim Boswell">Mr. Boswell</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0412P0-05089">To ask the Secretary of State for Education and Skills pursuant to his Answer of 17 September, reference 129985 what plans he has to harmonise reporting of work-based participation and success rates with sector skills council boundaries. [131571]</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0412P0-05090'>
        <a name='S6CV0412P0_20031027_CWS2_439'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-ivan-lewis' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0412P0_20031027_CWS2_439' title='Link to this speech by Mr Ivan Lewis' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-ivan-lewis" title="Mr Ivan Lewis">Mr. Ivan Lewis</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0412P0-05090">This is a matter for the Learning and Skills Council (LSCI. Mark Haysom the Council's Chief Executive will write to the hon. Member with the information requested and a copy of his reply will be placed in the Library.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
